items.definition: This group covers agricultural biotechnology.

prefLabel._value: Agricultural molecular engineering of nucleic acids and proteins
Genetically modified field crops and pasture

items.definition: This group covers the management of agriculture, land, farms and rural businesses.

prefLabel._value: Farm management, rural management and agribusiness
Agriculture, land and farm management not elsewhere classified

items.definition:
This group covers the sciences and technologies supporting the primary production of livestock, including birds and poultry.
It includes:
• bees and apiary culture;
• egg production; and
• animal production for domestic or sporting uses.

prefLabel._value: Crop and pasture biochemistry and physiology
Crop and pasture biomass and bioproducts
Crop and pasture improvement (incl. selection and breeding)
Crop and pasture post harvest technologies (incl. transportation and storage)
Crop and pasture protection (incl. pests, diseases and weeds)
Crop and pasture waste water use
Organic and low chemical input crop production
Crop and pasture production not elsewhere classified

items.definition: This group covers the sciences and technologies supporting fishing and production of freshwater and marine fisheries (including shellfish and crustaceans).
This group covers the food sciences.

prefLabel._value: Beverage chemistry and beverage sensory science
Food chemistry and food sensory science
Food safety, traceability, certification and authenticity

items.definition: This group covers forestry sciences and silviculture.
This group covers horticultural production and horticultural science.

prefLabel._value: Field organic and low chemical input horticulture
Horticultural crop improvement (incl. selection and breeding)
Horticultural crop protection (incl. pests, diseases and weeds)
Post harvest horticultural technologies (incl. transportation and storage)

items.definition: This group covers veterinary sciences practised on livestock for primary production, domestic, sporting and other uses.
This group covers agricultural and veterinary and food sciences not elsewhere classified.

prefLabel._value: Other agricultural, veterinary and food sciences
Other agricultural, veterinary and food sciences not elsewhere classified

items.definition: This division covers biological sciences.
This group covers biochemistry or the chemistry of living organisms. It includes bioinformatics, cell biology and membrane biology.

prefLabel._value: Cellular interactions (incl. adhesion, matrix, cell wall)
Proteomics and intermolecular interactions (excl. medical proteomics)
Biochemistry and cell biology not elsewhere classified

items.definition: This group covers bioinformatics and computational biology.

prefLabel._value: Bioinformatics and computational biology not elsewhere classified

items.definition: This group covers ecology other than its environmental applications.

prefLabel._value: Marine and estuarine ecology (incl. marine ichthyology)

items.definition: This group covers evolutionary biology, including biogeography and adaptation.

prefLabel._value: Plant and fungus systematics and taxonomy

items.definition: This group covers genetics and heredity.

prefLabel._value: Gene expression (incl. microarray and other genome-wide approaches)

items.definition: This group covers industrial biotechnology .

prefLabel._value: Industrial molecular engineering of nucleic acids and proteins

items.definition: This group covers microbiology, including bacteriology, parasitology and virology.

This group covers plant biology.
It includes:
• plant pathology other than that associated with plant protection procedures used in agriculture and horticulture; and
• phycology (including algae and marine grasses).
This group covers zoology.
